 122: ## Per-Worker Prompt File
 123: 
 124: Preserved in `prompts/<role>.prompt.md`. Contains the **exact text** sent as the `prompt` parameter to the Task tool.
 125: 
 126: This enables:
 127: - **Replay**: Re-run the same prompt to reproduce results
 128: - **Debugging**: Understand what the worker was told
 129: - **Improvement**: Refine prompts based on outcomes
 130: 
 131: ## Per-Worker Result File
 132: 
 133: Preserved in `results/<role>.result.md`. Contains the **full text** returned by the worker agent.
 134: 
 135: This enables:
 136: - **Audit**: Verify what the worker claimed vs. what actually happened
 137: - **Debugging**: Understand why a reviewer accepted or rejected
 138: - **Learning**: Identify patterns in successful vs. failed runs
