The build passed. The test runner itself is the problem now: Vitest is trying to fork processes in this sandbox and dies with `spawn EPERM` before it even collects files. I’m adding a local Vitest config to run the package tests in a single thread and to explicitly include the new `tests/*.test.ts` files.
